<div id="PageContent">

<h4>About the registry</h4>
<div class="indentLeft">
<p>
All Service Providers (SP) wishing to authenticate users via the University of Washington's Shibboleth Identity Provider (IdP)
must register for that service.  
<p>
<a href="https://wiki.cac.washington.edu/x/fiOD">Learn more about the registry</a>
</div>

<h4>Existing service providers</h4>
<div class="indentLeft">
<p>
The list on the left shows all service providers known to the University's IdP, including those 
registered with <a href="http://incommon.org/">InCommon</a> and those registered manually 
through this registry service.
<p>
Type part of an SP's entity id in the search window to filter the list.
</div>

<h4>New registration</h4>
<div class="indentLeft">
<p>
If you are the owner of a service providers's domain you can register that service provider with our IdP. 
Use the "New SP" link at the top of the service provider list.
</div>


